So here goes;
Decided to try CL to see if there's anyone normal out there. But what is normal nowadays? I'm looking for a man, a man who's not into games, not into taking advantage of a woman, not into lying each time he opens his mouth. Sounds fairly simple right? Not so much. 
I'm a white female, 50yrs young & my life is wonderful. Hows things w/ you? Not looking for anyone under 35. Respond if you have hopes & dreams of a good life. Everything else is just a waste of time.......
